legacy.full_text: @Blue_Sauron Seriously impressive but Nickelback for the soundtrack?  Really?  I thought you were trying to win this war. I'm a Canuck and think that's a bad plan. If you need acceptable tunes to describe a kinetic event try Bloodywood, Clutch, Priest, anything but them. Geez..🤣

@Blue_Sauron Those types of buildings are (or were) likely full of poultry of some kind, on what looks to be a modern farm. Painful to see people’s property and lives destroyed, yet again. Looking forward to the rebuild of 🇺🇦 when this shit is over- the world will not forget !!
